name: Squares #3
description:
These works are all made of squares and want to express the feeling of different cultures and lifestyles of human beings at the height of simplicity, so that everyone can see

Simple works that do not even have color and are designed with the simplest computer painting tools can look for a while to talk about the person seen in the work. How simple, creative and tasteful it can be. By purchasing these works individually and in one place, you can support my idea and art to display my other collections, each of which has important ideas for promotion in the community.
